<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>TanjiChat</title>
<style>
  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
  body {
    background: #0d1117;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .bg-circles {
    position: fixed; inset: 0; pointer-events: none; z-index: 0;
  }
  .circle {
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 50%;
    filter: blur(80px);
    opacity: 0.15;
  }
  .c1 { width: 500px; height: 500px; background: #2AABEE; top: -100px; left: -100px; animation: float1 8s ease-in-out infinite; }
  .c2 { width: 400px; height: 400px; background: #7B5EA7; bottom: -100px; right: -50px; animation: float2 10s ease-in-out infinite; }
  .c3 { width: 300px; height: 300px; background: #2AABEE; bottom: 100px; left: 200px; animation: float1 12s ease-in-out infinite reverse; }
  @keyframes float1 { 0%,100%{transform:translateY(0)} 50%{transform:translateY(-30px)} }
  @keyframes float2 { 0%,100%{transform:translateY(0)} 50%{transform:translateY(20px)} }

  .card {
    position: relative; z-index: 1;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 48px 40px;
    width: 380px;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 32px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
  }
  .logo {
    width: 72px; height: 72px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2AABEE, #7B5EA7);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 20px;
    font-size: 32px;
  }
  h1 { color: #fff; font-size: 26px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; letter-spacing: -0.5px; }
  p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 36px; line-height: 1.5; }

  .choices { display: flex; gap: 16px; }
  .choice-btn {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 20px 12px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
  }
  .choice-btn:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); border-color: rgba(42,171,238,0.5); background: rgba(42,171,238,0.08); }
  .choice-btn.female:hover { border-color: rgba(255,100,180,0.5); background: rgba(255,100,180,0.08); }
  .choice-icon { font-size: 40px; }
  .choice-name { color: #fff; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; }
  .choice-sub { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35); font-size: 12px; }

  .male-icon { color: #2AABEE; }
  .female-icon { color: #FF64B4; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="bg-circles">
  <div class="circle c1"></div>
  <div class="circle c2"></div>
  <div class="circle c3"></div>
</div>
<div class="card">
  <div class="logo">💬</div>
  <h1>TanjiChat</h1>
  <p>Aap kaun hain? Apna gender select karein chat shuru karne ke liye.</p>
  <div class="choices">
    <a href="/chat/tanji" class="choice-btn male">
      <span class="choice-icon">👦</span>
      <span class="choice-name">Tanji</span>
      <span class="choice-sub">Male</span>
    </a>
    <a href="/chat/hinata" class="choice-btn female">
      <span class="choice-icon">👧</span>
      <span class="choice-name">Hinata</span>
      <span class="choice-sub">Female</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
